{
  "stem": "7739.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He also obtained permits to work in these factories for my mother, my older sister, and of course, my older brother.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I was in the verge, I was, in 1942, I must have been around 11 years old-- no, I was 11, almost 13 years old then, in 1942.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was 11 when the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I also had a work permit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, my younger brother, we come back to my younger brother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He must have been about 11 then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was so smart in school, in cheder-- you know, we used to go to the [NON-ENGLISH] to the weekly portion of the-- of the-- of the Bible to go through, learn it.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And came around Thursday or Friday time, the teacher used to test you, how well you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When it came Friday, I wasn't that good, but my younger brother, he only had to study Monday and Tuesday and he knew it by heart everything else.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he was very smart.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I would say he was much smarter than me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "At the day-- at the day of the expulsion, he arranged-- not the day of the expulsion-- he arranged before for a Christian family, who were neighbors and old family friends, they should hide him out.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was agreed amongst all of us, we had work permits.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Either Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Kowacki-- who was supposed to come and take my brother and myself away on a Thursday-- the expulsion took place on a Tuesday.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we were stuck.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I used my work permit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother went to this Christian family at the day of the expulsion, which took place on the 27th of October, 1942.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Please explain for those of us who don't know what the expulsion meant.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
